\n<div class=\"kz-warning kz-screen-only\">\n  <strong>数据质量提示 / Data Quality Notes</strong>\n  <ul class=\"kz-list\">\n    <li>Gallup 模拟量表 A/B 双侧映射已完整（双侧计分题 98.3%，34/34 个主题参与计分）。结果为探索性参考，非官方 CliftonStrengths 报告。/ Gallup simulation has full A/B mapping (dual-side 98.3%, 34/34 themes scored). Results are for exploration—not an official CliftonStrengths report.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kz-synthesis\">\n  <h3>综合解读与给你的建议 | Summary & Recommendations</h3>\n  <p><strong>刘朗行</strong>，你好。以下是对你本次双维度测评的综合解读——帮你把「喜欢做什么」和「擅长怎么做」放在一起看。</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>Hello <strong>刘朗行</strong>. This section integrates what you enjoy doing with how you naturally work best.</em></p>\n\n  <h4>你是谁：兴趣舞台 + 优势风格 | Who You Are</h4>\n  <p>你的 Holland 三码是 <strong>ESA</strong>，兴趣舞台标签为 <strong>领导影响派 / Impact Driver</strong>；Gallup 主导优势领域是 <strong>影响力</strong>（次要领域：关系建立），工作风格偏向 <strong>推动影响型 / Influential Mobilizer</strong>。</p>\n  <p>Top 5 才干主题：行动、取悦、竞争、追求、自信</p>\n  <ul class=\"kz-list\">\n    <li><strong>E</strong>（企业型（Enterprising））— 最感兴趣：喜欢领导、说服、组织资源以实现目标，重视影响力与商业成就。</li>\n<li><strong>S</strong>（社会型（Social））— 次感兴趣：喜欢与人互动、帮助他人、教导或治疗，重视人际关系与社会贡献。</li>\n<li><strong>A</strong>（艺术型（Artistic））— 第三感兴趣：喜欢艺术、设计、音乐、写作或表演，重视自我表达、创造力和审美体验。</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>兴趣与优势如何配合 | How Interests & Strengths Fit</h4>\n  <p>你的 Gallup 主导领域（影响力）与 Holland 三码中的 E 型高度一致，说明你在相关方向上拥有内外双重能量支撑。 / Your leading Gallup domain (影响力) aligns strongly with the E type in your Holland code, giving you both internal motivation and natural ability in related directions.</p>\n  <p><strong>整体契合度 / Overall Fit</strong>：兴趣与优势高度一致 / High alignment</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-small\">三码在六边形上相对集中，兴趣轮廓较为清晰。/ Your three-letter code is relatively consistent on the hexagon.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"kz-synthesis-advice\">\n    <p><strong>给你的三条建议 / Three Recommendations for You</strong></p>\n    <ol class=\"kz-list\">\n      <li>主导或参与一个小型项目（活动、社团、售卖、演讲），体验说服与推动的过程。/ Lead or join a small project to experience persuasion, coordination, and momentum.</li><li>练习用 3 分钟清晰表达一个观点，并观察听众的反应——你的优势在「推动他人行动」。/ Practice expressing one idea clearly in 3 minutes and observe how others respond—your strength is mobilizing action.</li><li>你的兴趣与优势整体一致，可以较大胆地在主导交叉方向上投入时间；仍建议用实习或项目做小范围验证。/ Your interests and strengths align well—feel confident investing time in your primary intersection, but still validate through projects or internships.</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>结合以上解读，当前最值得你留意的探索方向包括：<strong>销售总监、培训师、创意总监</strong>。请从下方「稳妥入口职业」和「核心推荐专业」中挑选 1–2 个，用真实体验去验证——喜欢不等于适合，适合也需要在实践中确认。</p>\n  <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>Based on this profile, directions worth exploring include: <strong>销售总监、培训师、创意总监</strong>. Pick 1–2 from the safe-entry careers and core majors below, and validate through real experience.</em></p>\n\n  <div class=\"kz-ethics\">\n    <p><strong>重要提醒 / Important Reminder</strong>：本报告是<strong>探索与自我发现的辅助工具</strong>，不能替代你的判断，也不能限制你的可能性。测评结果会随经历与成长而变化——请带着好奇而非焦虑阅读，并与信任的老师、家长或咨询师讨论你的下一步。</p>\n    <p class=\"kz-en\"><em>This report is an <strong>exploration aid</strong>, not a verdict on who you must become. Results can evolve with experience—read with curiosity, not anxiety, and discuss your next steps with trusted adults or counselors.</em></p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"kz-type-card\" style=\"border-left: 6px solid #f59e0b;\">\n      <div class=\"kz-type-badges\">\n        <span class=\"kz-type-badge kz-holland-badge\" style=\"background:#f59e0b;\">ESA</span>\n        <span class=\"kz-type-plus\">+</span>\n        <span class=\"kz-type-badge kz-domain-badge\" style=\"background:#f59e0b;\">影响力</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kz-type-summary\">\n        <strong>领导影响派 / Impact Driver</strong> × <strong>推动影响型</strong>\n        <br><span class=\"kz-en\">Impact Driver × Influential Mobilizer</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n\n\n    <div class=\"kz-hero-illustration\">\n      <div class=\"kz-illustration-row\" style=\"margin:0;\">\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\" style=\"max-width:180px;\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <rect x=\"55\" y=\"75\" width=\"50\" height=\"8\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"50\" width=\"8\" height=\"25\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"75\" y=\"40\" width=\"8\" height=\"35\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"90\" y=\"55\" width=\"8\" height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <path d=\"M110 45 L120 35 L120 55 Z\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"125\" cy=\"45\" r=\"8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">领导影响派</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Impact Driver</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\" style=\"max-width:180px;\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <path d=\"M52 55 L52 75 L68 70 L68 50 Z\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <path d=\"M68 55 L95 48\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <path d=\"M95 35 L95 65\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      <ellipse cx=\"95\" cy=\"50\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"50\" r=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">影响力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Influencing</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kz-hero-text\">\n        <p><strong>你的组合画像 / Your Profile</strong></p>\n        <p>兴趣舞台：领导影响派（Impact Driver）；优势领域：影响力 / Influencing。</p>\n        <p class=\"kz-en\">Interest stage: Impact Driver; Leading strength domain: Influencing.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n\n<h2>1. 我的测评画像 | My Profile</h2>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Holland 兴趣六维得分 | RIASEC Scores</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">分数越高，代表该类型越能描述你的兴趣倾向 / Higher scores mean stronger alignment with that interest type.</div>\n  <svg width=\"100%\" height=\"224\" viewBox=\"0 0 420 224\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect x=\"70\" y=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#fee2e2\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"10\" width=\"110.20408163265307\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#ef4444\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"26.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">现实型 R</text><text x=\"188.20408163265307\" y=\"26.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">18</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"44\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#dbeafe\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"44\" width=\"91.83673469387756\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"60.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">研究型 I</text><text x=\"169.83673469387756\" y=\"60.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">15</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"78\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#ede9fe\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"78\" width=\"208.16326530612244\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#8b5cf6\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"94.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">艺术型 A</text><text x=\"286.1632653061224\" y=\"94.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">34</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"112\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#dcfce7\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"112\" width=\"251.02040816326533\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#22c55e\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"128.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">社会型 S</text><text x=\"329.0204081632653\" y=\"128.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">41</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"146\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"146\" width=\"300.0\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"162.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">企业型 E</text><text x=\"378.0\" y=\"162.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">49</text><rect x=\"70\" y=\"180\" width=\"300\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#f3f4f6\"/><rect x=\"70\" y=\"180\" width=\"79.59183673469389\" height=\"22\" rx=\"11\" fill=\"#6b7280\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"196.0\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">常规型 C</text><text x=\"157.59183673469389\" y=\"196.0\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" fill=\"#374151\">13</text></svg>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Gallup 优势领域 | CliftonStrengths Domains</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">主导领域是你最自然的工作方式，次要领域是其次 / Your leading domain is your most natural way of working.</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-domain-grid\">\n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#fee2e2; border-top: 4px solid #ef4444;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">执行力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Executing</div>\n          \n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#fef3c7; border-top: 4px solid #f59e0b;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">影响力</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Influencing</div>\n          <span class=\"kz-domain-badge kz-domain-primary\">主导</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#dcfce7; border-top: 4px solid #22c55e;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">关系建立</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Relationship Building</div>\n          <span class=\"kz-domain-badge kz-domain-secondary\">次要</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-domain-block\" style=\"background:#dbeafe; border-top: 4px solid #3b82f6;\">\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-name\">战略思维</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-domain-en\">Strategic Thinking</div>\n          \n        </div>\n        </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kz-chart-card\">\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-title\">Top 5 才干主题 | My Top 5 Themes</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-chart-subtitle\">颜色代表该主题所属的优势领域 / Colors show which domain each theme belongs to.</div>\n  <div class=\"kz-top5-pills\">\n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">1</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">行动</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">2</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">取悦</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">3</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">竞争</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">4</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">追求</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"kz-top5-pill\" style=\"background:#f59e0b20; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; color:#f59e0b;\">\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-rank\">5</span>\n          <span class=\"kz-top5-name\">自信</span>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>2. 我的核心结果 | My Core Results</h2>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>维度 / Dimension</th><th>结果 / Result</th></tr>\n  <tr><td>Holland 三码 / Holland Code</td><td><strong>ESA</strong> — 企业型（Enterprising）</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>优势领域 / Leading Strength Domain</td><td>影响力</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>优势风格 / Strengths Style</td><td>推动影响型 / Influential Mobilizer</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n\n        <div class=\"kz-illustration-card\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <rect width=\"160\" height=\"120\" rx=\"12\" fill=\"#fef3c7\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"60\" r=\"28\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" opacity=\"0.15\"/>\n      <rect x=\"55\" y=\"75\" width=\"50\" height=\"8\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"60\" y=\"50\" width=\"8\" height=\"25\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"75\" y=\"40\" width=\"8\" height=\"35\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <rect x=\"90\" y=\"55\" width=\"8\" height=\"20\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <path d=\"M110 45 L120 35 L120 55 Z\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"125\" cy=\"45\" r=\"8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n    </svg>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-label\">领导影响派</div>\n          <div class=\"kz-illustration-en\">Impact Driver</div>\n        </div>\n        \n\n<h2>3. 稳妥入口职业 | Safe Entry Points</h2>\n<p>如果你更关注就业稳定性和现实可行性，以下方向是不错的起点。</p>\n<p class=\"kz-en\">If you prioritize employment stability and practical entry paths, these roles are good starting points.</p>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>职业 / Career</th><th>标签 / Tag</th><th>相关专业 / Related Majors</th></tr>\n  \n        <tr>\n          <td>创意总监</td>\n          <td><span class=\"kz-tag kz-tag-explore\">探索型 / Explore-oriented</span></td>\n          <td>广告学、视觉传达、设计管理、市场营销、传播学</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>培训师</td>\n          <td><span class=\"kz-tag kz-tag-explore\">探索型 / Explore-oriented</span></td>\n          <td>教育学、人力资源管理、心理学、企业管理、传播学</td>\n        </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>4. 核心推荐专业 | Core Recommended Majors</h2>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>专业 / Major</th><th>国内可报说明 / Domestic Note</th><th>海外方向（以英国为例）/ Overseas Example (UK)</th></tr>\n  \n        <tr>\n          <td>市场营销</td>\n          <td>按具体院校招生目录查询</td>\n          <td>建议按具体院校查询 / Check programme titles</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n       